@startuml
title UC11 - Chatbot Request State
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Validating : user submits question
Validating --> Rejected : not logged in / too long / write request
Validating --> WaitingProvider : allowed
WaitingProvider --> Answered : provider returns response
WaitingProvider --> Failed : timeout/unavailable
Answered --> Idle
Failed --> Idle : user may retry later
Rejected --> Idle
@enduml
